I was having severe tooth infection with swelling and immediately checked online for the nearest dentist and then I came across Dr Beena Gopi  , I immediately booked an appointment and went to meet her with the intention of extracting my tooth coz I could not handle it anymore ,  Dr Beena had explained to me the importance of saving my tooth so I opted for the Root Canal treatment , I am super impressed that it did not pain at all while or after the treatment , I had my crown been fixed few days back and I’m perfectly back to normal , her fees are very reasonable , highly recommend Dr Beena Gopi to all you guys . 

A big thank u to Sangeeta too who is doctors assistant .

Doctor was kind hearted, polite and very knowledgeable. She explained the cause of my problem and how it could be resolved. It was very well explained. The whole treatment procedure was done very gently and it wasn't tough for me to go through it. At the end she explained how the problem recurrence can be prevented with some easy steps. At the time of this pandemic we are going through, doc took all necessary steps to take care of patients safety. In end I would say that I was very satisfied with care and treatment I recieved. Thank you

The doctor was very patient and explained the procedure and also checked if I have any other problem in my mouth and also explained the root canal treatment step by step. I am very satisfied with my treatment. I did not feel any pain and I am very happy with how my cap looks ..fits just perfect and looks very natural..I highly recommend this place for any dental treatment. I know I am going to ask my friends to go here as I am confident their treatment would be satisfactory just like mine. Thank you for fixing my teeth Dr.Beena Gopi😁😁😁
